commit.message:
match filterText with textEdit

Signed-off-by: Yan Zhang <yanzh@microsoft.com>

Build workspace action can report progress to client

Signed-off-by: Sheng Chen <sheche@microsoft.com>

Allow renaming lambda parameters

Signed-off-by: Snjezana Peco <snjezana.peco@redhat.com>

Update m2e to 1.15.0.20200304-0718

Signed-off-by: Fred Bricon <fbricon@gmail.com>

Provide diagnostics and quickfix when open non-project java file

Signed-off-by: Jinbo Wang <jinbwan@microsoft.com>

Support lazy loading invisible project

Signed-off-by: Jinbo Wang <jinbwan@microsoft.com>

Use more stable update sites in TP

See #1370

This reverts commit 2eb0ab282234822bedd175536dc5c7bebd5171a9.

Add changelog for 0.52.0

Signed-off-by: Fred Bricon <fbricon@gmail.com>

BadLocationException and diagnostic with negative line number send to client

Signed-off-by: Snjezana Peco <snjezana.peco@redhat.com>

Use stable lsp4j 0.9.0 release

Signed-off-by: Snjezana Peco <snjezana.peco@redhat.com>
Also-by: Fred Bricon <fbricon@gmail.com>

Add GRADLE_USER_HOME preference

Signed-off-by: Snjezana Peco <snjezana.peco@redhat.com>

j.i.gradle.arguments and j.i.gradle.jvmArguments aren't properly defined

Signed-off-by: Snjezana Peco <snjezana.peco@redhat.com>

Use stable version for JDT/Platform, for now

Signed-off-by: Fred Bricon <fbricon@gmail.com>

Update the root path on workspace folder change event (#1389)

fixes #1388

Signed-off-by: Sheng Chen <sheche@microsoft.com>
